name: amptools
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.1.11" %}

package:
  name: amptools
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/usgs/shakemap-amp-tools/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 48d7c178ca3567062d4ed15e766311b4c9fea05fae8aade745acbf30bf5fc525

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv

requirements:
  build:
    - python >=3.6
    - pip
  run:
    - python =3.6
    - h5py >2.7.1
    - gmprocess >0.2.7
    - configobj

test:

  imports:
    - amptools

about:
  home: https://github.com/usgs/shakemap-amp-tools
  license: Public Domain
  summary: 'Fetch and process strong motion waveform/peak amplitude data.'
  license_family: Public Domain
  license_file: LICENSE.md

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - mhearne-usgs
    - hschovanec-usgs
